openapi: 3.0.0
host: localhost:8080
paths:
  /api/enum:
    get:
      parameters:
        - in: query
          name: x
          schema:
            type: string
            enum: [foo, bar]
        - in: query
          name: y
          schema:
            type: integer
            enum: [42, 1234567]
    post:
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/EnumDto'
components:
  schemas:
    EnumDto:
      type: Object
      properties:
        values:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
            enum: [foo, bar]
